<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">عُرْوَةُ قَبْلَ التَّأَهُّبِ لِلرَّحِيل:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>أَسُوقُ إِلَيْكِ يَا عَفْرَا سَلاَمِي<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">عَفْرَاء:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>سَلاَمٌ يَا فَتى العَرَبِ الْكِرَامِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>{هَاشِمٌ الرِّفَاعِي / في مَسْرَحِيَّتِةِ الشِّعْرِيَّةِ <span class="c1">" عُرْوَةَ بْنِ حِزَام "</span> بِتَصَرُّف}<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
